{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2374031, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我已經有兩個了", "timestamp": 1630128066, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374032, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有且好就写，没有就别自取其辱", "timestamp": 1630128066, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374036, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "SRT基本上就是看看，甚至有的项目连看看都没有", "timestamp": 1630128101, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374046, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374032, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: “好”大概是啥程度？比如gpa3.85可以写吗", "timestamp": 1630128154, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374049, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374036, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 如果想找一个能自己做科研发文章的srt，有建议吗", "timestamp": 1630128186, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374051, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374049, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: SRT一般没有这种东西，就是看别人搬砖，有的老师都不让你看别人搬砖", "timestamp": 1630128211, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374053, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374049, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 本科生发不了文章的，尤其大一大二", "timestamp": 1630128240, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374059, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374046, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 看你们院系的一般情况了，3.85一般排名是中游偏上一点？这样就没必要写", "timestamp": 1630128302, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374084, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "到时候报名阶段报名就行了吧，到时候发个邮件说一下也行。如果现在自己有想法，当然可以找老师提前商量，让老师帮忙立个项", "timestamp": 1630128559, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374177, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374059, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 大概在班上排30%，系里10%", "timestamp": 1630129076, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374084, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: ok谢谢啦", "timestamp": 1630129154, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374357, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当别人说本科生发不了文章的时候，你找到一个能发文章的SRT就赢了", "timestamp": 1630130691, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374421, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374357, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 对 我其实也是这个想法。大一社工志愿什么的做的太多了，翘课也比较多。大二准备好好学习，看能不能有点优势", "timestamp": 1630131285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2374424, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374357, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 只是不知道如果研究生方向不同的话，srt还有用吗", "timestamp": 1630131317, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374424, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: srt只是带你做研究，了解一下科研的思路等等，就算方向不一样但很多方法是相通的，表现你有科研的能力。就好像转系要求高的GPA，其实也只是对学习能力的考量，并不很在乎你实质学的是什么", "timestamp": 1630146109, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2376141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 453496, "reply_to": 2374424, "tag": null, "text": "建议大二可以先整个srt试试水体验一下，大三的时候往自己喜欢的方向靠，找老师立个srt或者自己找老师进组", "timestamp": 1630146174, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 453496, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "零字班想做srt，和老师没有任何接触，发邮件时需要注意啥？需要写上自己的条件（gpa、科创经历）吗？", "timestamp": 1630128034, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1630146173, "url": "", "vote": {}}}